            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Being a proud student of DAV Brij Vihar, i really am thankful to my respected Principal sir, teachers & mates for providing me with the bestest environment i could ever get.\nSchool isn't only for teaching bookish knowledge, but to enrich us with the valuable life lessons, &  that's why our respected Principal sir provides us with the bestest of valuable lessons on a daily basis in school assembly. Along with these precious teachings, we're doing great in sports, singing, dancing & other curricular activities too.\nBeing taught by our hardworking, knowledgeable & nice teachers, it has really been a great & memorable experience.\nDAV Brij Vihar is really an amazing institution & I'm thankful to this school from the core of my heart for making all the students the better version of ourselves.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
