            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I attended this school more than a decade and have only great things to say about my experience. The teachers are amazing and cooperative, the curriculum is second to none and each student is treated with care.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
