            "name": "SOUMMYA KARMAKAR"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-04-13",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I passed nearly a decade ago from DAV Brij Vihar and have only great things to say about my experience. The teachers are amazing, the curriculum is second to none and each child is treated with care. The administration is open minded and think outside the box to make DAV Brij Vihar a successful educational experience for the students. DAV Brij Vihar is committed to the whole child. They teach value lessons, communication and leadership skills. Patriotism is also present in their activities.",
          "publisher": {
